>> title: Roasted Broccoli
>> cuisine: American
>> tags: vegetable, vegan, gluten-free, soy-free
>> servings: 4
>> yield: 4 cups
>> storage_days: 4
>> storage_method: refrigerated
>> reheat: Microwave or serve at room temperature.

Preheat #oven{} to 425F (220C).

Cut @broccoli{2%heads} into florets.

Toss broccoli with @olive oil{3%tbsp}, @garlic{4%cloves}(smashed), @kosher salt{1%tsp}, and @red pepper flakes{1/2%tsp} in #large bowl{}.

Spread on #sheet pan{} in a single layer.

Roast ~{20-25%minutes} until charred and crispy at edges.

Squeeze @lemon{1%wedge}(juice) over top before serving.

Let cool and store in #airtight container{}.

-- Used in: Mac & cheese side, bowls, as a side dish
